User Side

1 -> User can register
2 -> After register user must be login into the system
3 -> After login user can their profile details and delete their own account
4 -> User can view their all task list by duedate sorting (important task is first).
5 -> User can add their task detail such as (title,description,startdate,duedate,User refercen Obejct id)
6 -> User can change their task detail as per user requirement
7 -> If task is completed User can delete their task detail as per user requirement


Admin Side

1 -> Admin can view all kinds of user details and as per admin requirement their can change user information and delete user details
2 -> Admin can view all the task detail


Authentication

1 -> JWT Token based authentication
2 -> Without authentication only three url work (/login,/register,/admin)